title: The Best of...What's Left of...Not Only but Also...The Video
creator_credit: BBC, Dick Clement, James Gilbert, Joe McGrath and John Street
brief_description: After 20 years apart, Peter Cook and Dudley Moore reunite and share their past memories of their comedy partnership together. We see many old comedy routines that they performed together.
